title:
BIDU-SW (09888.HK) Recedes 5%, as CN Media Says AI Partnership w/ Apple Not 
Yet Confirmed
text: BIDU-SW (09888.HK)  +3.250 (+3.268%)    Short selling $113.46M; Ratio 12.994%    opened down 2.78% today, and once sank 5.27% to a low of $98.9. It last printed at $99.65, descending 4.55%, with a volume of 3.0244 million shares and a turnover of $304 million.It was earlier reported that BIDU will provide AI functionality for the Chinese versions of Apple's (AAPL.US)       iPhone 16, Mac system, and iOS 18, which will be released this year. However, a source close to Apple, cited by China Daily, denied this, saying the two companies have not yet nailed a partnership.(HK stocks quote is delayed for at least 15 mins.Short Selling Data as at 2024-03-28 16:25.)
